cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DB 

The paper deals with training a classifier to detect the encyclopedic intent of web queries, which is a task related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of knowledge bases such as Freebase and Wikipedia also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves the analysis of large sets of data, which could be relevant to database systems (cs.DB).
